data.description: Beautiful, spacious home in White Bear Lake.  As you walk in, you will notice the west facing living room that receives an abundance of natural light.   Hardwood floors.  Main floor sun room with vaulted ceilings.  3 bedrooms on the upper floor.  Great office/flex space that could also be used as a non-confirming 4th bedroom.   The lower level makes for a great place to hang out for a movie night.  Fenced back yard and the deck/patio is a great space to host summer BBQs.  Freshly painted interior and newer roof.  Come take a look today!
